With letters and speeches, by the late Duke of Buckingham, the Honourable Henry Savile, Esq; Sir George Etherridge, to several persons of honour. And letters by several eminent hands. Rochester, John Wilmot, Earl of, 1647-1680. Savile, Henry, 1642-1687. Brown, Thomas, 1663-1704. Buckingham, George Villiers, Duke of, 1628-1687.

Bound and filmed following R1745A (Familiar letters vol. I). Reproduction of original in: Universität Göttingen Bibliothek.
